Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 在四國至九州的太平洋沿岸之間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多名目擊者看到了神秘的發光現象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有群眾說聽到了類似爆炸的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當做隕石來處理了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要是隕石墜落到自己所住的地方的話 就可以瞬間解脫了」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種自殺性的帖子意外的多呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(652,412)\3c&H4D5A42&\c&HD5D6D1&\shad0\bord2.5}神秘的巨大隕石墜落？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也確認到了觀測史上最大的太陽耀斑活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據專家…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大規模的太陽耀斑活動？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 目前要做的是如何解決小華不在的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是能唯一能預知到敵人行動的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小華預知到敵人有所行動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會馬上通知我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺可以賭上魔法少女的名譽作保證
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 如果她被敵人抓到的話就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小華驅動了布盧姆的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個事實被洩露的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有更多的人盯上她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼沒有阻止小華？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小華！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:50.95,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この町を生きていくすべなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:50.95,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拯救這個城市的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:58.25,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない夢を見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:58.25,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著一個沒有終點的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:04.41,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だって　見てるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:04.41,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣 懷著這樣的夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:12.22,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠いようで　ずっと近くに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:12.22,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似是遠在天邊 又近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:18.27,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だって　見えるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:18.27,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣 看到那個希望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:27.43,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普段言えないことも　口にしてみること
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:27.43,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐露平時說不出口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:35.58,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑んでいくこと　二本の足で立つこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:35.58,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙腿立直站起來 勇敢地做出挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:48.97,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空照らした　始まりのイナズマ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:48.97,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是照亮夜空的最初一剎閃電
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:55.52,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここの戦いが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:55.52,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:02.87,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この町を生きていくすべなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:02.87,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拯救這個城市的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:11.64,OP_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必ずこの夢を叶えるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:11.64,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的夢想一定會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得 昨天所使用的生命力光束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消耗了殘存能量的多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經讓阿朗佐對估算結果進行修正
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不對我們的作戰造成致命問題就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果讓人滿意就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的攻擊 布盧姆的能量也應該快耗盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一他們將Livlaster當作能量源的話 就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果公主殿下不在的話 他們就無法驅動…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的能量也是一大問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快一些將SIREN大人迎接回來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情都交給我們來做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家各有各的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許這顆星球給我們帶來了奇怪的影響…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的奇異能力能感受到SIREN大人的所在地嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反正是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不准呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:36.58,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDFDFD&\pos(640,498)}真正的{\c&HEABAC2&}自{\c&HFDFDFD&}我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星齒輪裝置的王族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有操縱生命力能量的特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓小華成為操縱Livlaster的生命體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正是用王族的因子製造她出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小華能驅動賜予她的Livlaster的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布盧姆應該就可以成為實戰兵器了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在最重要的是小華在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在小華關掉了通訊器 我們就只能等她主動聯絡我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盲目地去找也不會有任何進展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一樣擔心她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小華 你到底去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 原來還有一隻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀哦呀 我記得你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊拉啊拉 你好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是畫家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在是流浪者 所以我需要錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉帕的畫 出乎意料的很好賣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流浪民嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個人 我想一直和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我突然間害怕和他在一起了 所以就逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是逃出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦與他人有過深的交際 就會感受到他人的可怕之處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受風是一件很舒服的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上 有很多美好的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:07:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 人際關係是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿真心出來深交的話 絕對會受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地是可以信賴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的名字叫大地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 我已經按照您的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將第三開發部的數據傳送到了您的個人服務器中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 今晚你沒有什麼預定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 我們去吃個飯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我要忙私事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次再一起去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:08:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 您有什麼吩咐的話 請隨時叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KILL-T-GANG襲來的時候 Machine Goodfellow肯定會啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命力能量罐和KILL-T-GANG之間到底有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是久部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被別人擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這人不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也小心點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被他們發現的話就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是壞人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 得快點逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死胡同…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮兹就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把你也捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你看起來很精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底就是因為你跑了 我們才這麼辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂我說的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂吧？公主殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮兹！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布盧姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱的事為什麼每天都在增加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個冷血的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然對小仁美的邀請毫不動情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是【我】的話一定不會拒絕她的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所謂的【我】到底指的是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到您的聲音裡透著煩躁感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出將Machine Goodfellow的實證實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全權交給阿瑪拿和莫可的人可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們和KILL-T-GANG之間到底是怎樣的關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將Legacy墜落的人是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密是生活的必要組成部分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要將其藏好卻是件很困難的事呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什麼目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得到什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你不再煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區的機械！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急停止按鈕？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你真的認為那東西還有效嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個很好操縱的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來自小華的呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是仲夏騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是夢塔華…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我也不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再關閉電源了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追蹤她的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有聽到隊長的指示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了不要在關掉通信器了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢塔華…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是戰鬥單位中的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要服從你的上司 隊長的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天生命力能量不會有較大的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮兹受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始 就無法預知敵人的動向了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小華？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AMAROK來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛MALKIN也在這！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長一個人去過於危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然生命力能量不會流動的話 俺也過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你們兩個！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副司令負責去聯絡隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要找的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你待在這裡的話 是不會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你一直以來的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 我給您端茶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動了…動了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有追來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小華！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AMAROK和MALKIN呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛雖然被他們發現了 但卻沒有追來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太突然了 我好吃驚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決了一個巨大的煩惱 真是如獲重生的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我期盼已久的真正的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕克是不會說謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在做啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拍電影？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡藏著攝像機嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的自我覺醒的感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等行星齒輪裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是揭示世界之夢之人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎樣做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛你好像一直和布盧姆一起行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子就是布盧姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我需要向你們瞭解一些實情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Engine系列應該也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也出動Machine Goodfellow吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地原來都知道了啊 真正的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知小華和布盧姆一起被製造出來這事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得會是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會覺得很噁心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法應該已經傳遞給你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再一個人的鑽牛角尖 獨自悲傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 謝謝你拯救了種子島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這氣氛很難過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正AMAROK他們也不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小華帶著皮兹藏起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上 哲平!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:17:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Machine Goodfellow出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長和哲平正在和它進行交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也在跟進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是MM車並沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 也許他們另有目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 請把Earth Engine發射過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛Nebula也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一起送過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, Nebula Engine…射出！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷達上出現的Machine Goodfellow一共有兩架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請打足十二分的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩架？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到公主殿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的動作太快了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦熟悉了神經操演系統 倒也挺好用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earth…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nebula也來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二對一雖然不太公平…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們還是上吧 哲平！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 都給我停手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你們動一下的話 我就幹掉公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有邪惡軍團的感覺呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶著自己放棄永生的悔恨去死吧 ALBION！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆…為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這團光芒…難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命力能量…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小華？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Blossom嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢傷害我的同伴…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在控制光束？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把Livlaster已經進化成Ecdysic Mode了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(810,660)}羽              化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是皮兹的份！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑪拿！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再被生命力光束打中的話 機體會承受不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是永遠不會缺少驚喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在先看看皮兹怎樣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 皮兹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.53,0:22:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:11.28,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ頼りないその手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:11.28,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出還不夠可靠的手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:17.12,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君とあの虹の始まりを追いかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:17.12,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起 奔跑著追逐那道彩虹的發端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:21.54,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手を繋ぐ雨上がりの空には
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:21.54,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手牽手立在雨後的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:27.44,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸い込まれるような青さが広がって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:27.44,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邊無際的一片蒼藍深邃得要被淹沒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:32.18,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額（滲む汗と）揺れて（なびく髪に）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:32.18,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額頭上滲出的汗珠 微風下飄逸的秀髮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:37.32,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何故か（君が消えて）しまう（気がしたんだ）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:37.32,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 你似是在我面前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.98,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは（おかしいよね）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.98,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:45.11,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけと（一緒なの）　君は（知ってでも）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:45.11,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這並不要緊 就算你知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:48.36,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この星で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:48.36,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:50.89,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏の空を見上げてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:50.89,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望夏天的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:53.77,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人は時を止める
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:53.77,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的時間在這一刻停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:56.13,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あのさ　君とどれくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:59.08,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 我還可以跟你在一起多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.34,0:23:59.08,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒に居られるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:01.32,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思うよりもずっと早く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:01.32,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻比預想來得更早
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:04.24,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その手を握りしめる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:04.24,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我緊握住你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.47,0:24:06.59,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の顔は見えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.47,0:24:06.59,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有看到你的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:09.74,ED_SYL,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの時気付けなかった、
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:09.74,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究是沒有察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星齒輪裝置依靠覺醒後SIREN的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.67,0:24:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始製造新的生命力能量罐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.54,0:24:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KILL-T-GANG AIATAR前來襲擊地球
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.62,0:24:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 仲夏騎士團的作戰也進入了新的階段
